query: SELECT id, name, nameHe, date, time, FROM_UNIXTIME(date/1000) as readable_date FROM trip_routes WHERE tripId = (SELECT id FROM trips WHERE name LIKE '%סלובקיה%' LIMIT 1) ORDER BY date;
